  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>/!DISCLAIMER/![/b]</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kingdom of Rhea was born in 2016 and had the promise of becoming a souls like AA ARPG.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>After working for several years, here is the most complete version of the project to date.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kingdoms of Rhea will have been exhibited at Paris Games Week 2019, Japan Expo and many other events. However, we are putting the project on hold for the moment, hoping to resume it later, with more human and financial resources.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Souls like 3rd person action game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You will unlock skills with each defeated boss allowing you to venture deeper into the dungeon.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033700/extras/0064128567ebf47741a2708386d5386b.poster.avif?t=1729238136\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033700/extras/0064128567ebf47741a2708386d5386b.webm?t=1729238136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033700/extras/0064128567ebf47741a2708386d5386b.mp4?t=1729238136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><strong>DUBBING</strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The entire game is dubbed in French by:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pierre Alain de Guarrigues (Bragaan) </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Zarkiel (Gogo)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Barbara Damide (Dura) </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033700/extras/17d706df480bb578dd39935303f86312.poster.avif?t=1729238136\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033700/extras/17d706df480bb578dd39935303f86312.webm?t=1729238136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033700/extras/17d706df480bb578dd39935303f86312.mp4?t=1729238136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><strong>BOSS</strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Each boss will have unique and different skills, it's up to you to adapt to try to defeat them</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033700/extras/a62d77452dd81d9b897695aafbe7a20e.poster.avif?t=1729238136\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033700/extras/a62d77452dd81d9b897695aafbe7a20e.webm?t=1729238136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033700/extras/a62d77452dd81d9b897695aafbe7a20e.mp4?t=1729238136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong></p>",
